<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 01:07:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币的 24 小时承诺受到地缘政治现实检验</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-s-24-hour-promise-gets-a-geopolitical-reality-check</link><description>长期以来，比特币一直被宣传为提供其他市场无法提供的东西：24 小时实时了解全球风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4AG3wmEmoho/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 17:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-s-24-hour-promise-gets-a-geopolitical-reality-check</guid></item><item><title>随着市场波动加剧，比特币涨至 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/bitcoin-advances-toward-70-000-as-volatility-increases</link><description>随着中东战争不断升级，全球金融市场波动性加剧，比特币推向近期交易区间的上限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifHg170SjOsQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 16:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/bitcoin-advances-toward-70-000-as-volatility-increases</guid></item><item><title>银行监管机构采取措施限制美国稳定币奖励</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</link><description>美国货币监理署提出规则，限制公司通过白标平台推出品牌稳定币并提供与之相关的奖励，这是该机构为实施唐纳德·特朗普总统于 7 月签署的联邦加密货币法的首次重大尝试。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iF__U9SRvdHk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 22:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</guid></item><item><title>稳定币发行人 Tether 使用德勤提供 USAT 储备报告</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/stablecoin-issuer-tether-uses-deloitte-for-usat-reserve-report</link><description>多年来，Tether Holdings SA 一直表示主要会计师事务所不愿意提供审计服务，但现在，Tether Holdings SA 收到了德勤对其 USAT 稳定币有史以来第一份准备金报告的认可​​，该报告是为了遵守美国新法规而推出的。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igbJWXXDFJAo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 20:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/stablecoin-issuer-tether-uses-deloitte-for-usat-reserve-report</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略通过使用普通股加大比特币购买力度</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/saylor-s-strategy-mstr-steps-up-bitcoin-btc-buys-by-using-common-shares</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了价值超过 2 亿美元的比特币，并转向普通股为其大部分收购提供资金，尽管承诺将依靠其永久优先股。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ie1Zx_V76eOQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/saylor-s-strategy-mstr-steps-up-bitcoin-btc-buys-by-using-common-shares</guid></item><item><title>由于油价预示着风险，加密货币交易者感到提心吊胆</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-traders-on-tenterhooks-as-oil-prices-signal-risks</link><description>随着美国市场在中东爆炸事件后重新开放，数字资产交易谨慎，交易员关注石油、股票和货币的连锁反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irLFdjIcn3HI/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 03:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-traders-on-tenterhooks-as-oil-prices-signal-risks</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击引发不确定性，加密货币面临压力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-01/bitcoin-btc-recovery-looks-tepid-as-iran-strikes-stir-uncertainty</link><description>周末美国和以色列对伊朗的袭击动摇了投资者的信心，导致加密货币面临压力，交易者等待全球传统市场的指示。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9yiM3Ul6pt0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 07:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-01/bitcoin-btc-recovery-looks-tepid-as-iran-strikes-stir-uncertainty</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 伊朗赌注达 5.29 亿美元，新钱包大获全胜</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/polymarket-iran-bets-hit-529-million-as-new-wallets-draw-notice</link><description>随着本周末美国和以色列的炸弹落在伊朗身上，Polymarket 上的投注者（其中与袭击时间相关的合同交易额达 5.29 亿美元）开始获利。区块链侦探几乎立即开始在最近的投注中寻找不寻常的模式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.fUiA15VPBE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 21:24:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/polymarket-iran-bets-hit-529-million-as-new-wallets-draw-notice</guid></item><item><title>伊朗领导人去世后比特币恢复至 68,000 美元以上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</link><description>在伊朗证实该国最高领导人在美国和以色列的军事行动中被杀后，比特币和其他加密货币在周日亚洲早盘交易中大幅反弹。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivFEZEB6t.QU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 07:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</guid></item></channel></rss>